EXISTS (SELECT * FROM AD_Column c WHERE AD_Table.AD_Table_ID=c.AD_Table_ID AND c.ColumnName='Posted')
C_BPartner.IsVendor='Y' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM M_Product_PO po WHERE C_BPartner.C_BPartner_ID=po.C_BPartner_ID)

(EXISTS (SELECT * FROM C_BPartner bp WHERE AD_User.C_BPartner_ID=bp.C_BPartner_ID AND (bp.IsEmployee='Y')) OR AD_User.C_BPartner_ID IS NULL)
